# Build automation tool:
dnf make
# GNU compiler collection:
dnf gcc
# Core plugins for DNF:
dnf dnf-plugins-core
# Auto-rebuild kernel modules on updates:
dnf dkms
# Isolated installer for Python CLI apps:
dnf pipx
# UNIX shell (command interpreter):
dnf zsh
# X11 clipboard CLI:
dnf xclip
# Clone of "cat" with syntax highlighting and Git integration:
dnf bat
# Modern CLI resource monitor:
dnf btop
# System info fetch (like neofetch but in C):
dnf fastfetch
# System restore snapshots:
dnf timeshift
# TUI for Git:
dnf lazygit
# Modern GPU-accelerated terminal emulator:
dnf ghostty
# Open-source code editor:
dnf code
# Control PC fans/cooling curves:
dnf coolercontrol
# Extra GNOME settings:
dnf gnome-tweaks
# Password manager:
flatpak org.keepassxc.KeePassXC
# Manager GNOME extensions:
flatpak com.mattjakeman.ExtensionManager
# Messaging app:
flatpak org.telegram.desktop
# Voice and text chat software:
flatpak com.discordapp.Discord
# Markdown-based note-taking:
flatpak md.obsidian.Obsidian
# Firefox-based Web browser:
flatpak app.zen_browser.zen
# Lightweight BitTorrent client:
flatpak com.transmissionbt.Transmission
# Image editor (like Paint):
flatpak be.alexandervanhee.gradia
# Run Windows software via Wine containers:
flatpak com.usebottles.bottles
# GNOME videos player:
flatpak org.gnome.Totem
# Simple music player:
flatpak io.bassi.Amberol
# GUI frontend for the yt-dlp:
flatpak org.nickvision.tubeconverter
# Media converter:
flatpak io.gitlab.adhami3310.Converter
# Open-source office suite:
flatpak org.onlyoffice.desktopeditors
# Lossless video/audio cutter:
flatpak no.mifi.losslesscut
# Flatpak permissions manager GUI:
flatpak com.github.tchx84.Flatseal
# Flatpak package manager with GUI:
flatpak io.github.flattool.Warehouse
# System monitor (like Windows Task Manager):
flatpak io.missioncenter.MissionCenter
